<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَلَا يَسْقُطُ فِعْلُهَا مَا دَامَ العَقْلُ ثَابِتاً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ طَرَأَ عَجْزٌ أَوْ قُدْرَةٌ فِي أَثْنَائِهَا:</span> انْتَقَلَ وَبَنَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُسَنُّ قَصْرُ الرُّبَاعِيَّةِ فِي:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> سَفَرٍ طَوِيلٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> مُبَاحٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَيَقْضِي صَلَاةَ سَفَرٍ فِي حَضَرٍ،<span class="c5"> وَعَكْسُهُ:</span> تَامَّةً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ نَوَى:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- إِقَامَةً مُطْلَقَةً بِمَوْضِعٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- أَوْ <span class="c2">(١)</span> أَكْثَرَ مِنْ أَرْبَعَةِ أَيَّامٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- أَوِ ائْتَمَّ بِمُقِيمٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَتَمَّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَإِنْ حُبِسَ ظُلْماً،<span class="c5"> أَوْ لَمْ يَنْوِ إِقَامَةً:</span> قَصَرَ أَبَداً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُبَاحُ لَهُ الجَمْعُ:</span> بَيْنَ الظُّهْرَيْنِ والعِشَاءَيْنِ بِوَقْتِ إِحْدَاهُمَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (مطلقة بموضع أو) هو في (ب): في بلد.</p> </div>